{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782486779052,"sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_3EPR4X96tQnEq1WMwaXS7wGC","state":{"status":"error","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-research agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/lineages/gpt55fast\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55fast-1782485686835-ykwdkd\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: research\n  research_topic: For each of the five sk-design sub-skills (design-interface, design-foundations, design-motion, design-audit, design-md-generator), determine the highest-leverage expansions to their references and assets. Ground every recommendation in (1) the prior corpus research at .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/research.md and gap-analysis.md, and (2) the 43-entry external corpus at .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/external/. Also inspect each mode current references and assets under .opencode/skills/sk-design. For each mode produce: (a) inventory gaps such as thin or stale references and missing references or assets; (b) prioritized additions, each with type (reference or asset), title, why it raises usefulness, exact corpus sources, and effort; (c) an explicit do-NOT-add list where expansion is not effective, honoring the if-effective bar. Out of scope: taxonomy and architecture (already decided), net-new sub-skills, and any implementation. Deliverable: a per-mode expansion matrix in research.md.\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/lineages/gpt55fast via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/lineages/gpt55fast. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/lineages/gpt55fast.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55fast","specFolder":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55fast-1782485686835-ykwdkd","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"error":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782485686835-ykwdkd\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782485686835-ykwdkd\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55fast-1782485686835-ykwdkd\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 226,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","time":{"start":1782486760852,"end":1782486779048}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c3ac4d008f44520016a3e96d09da88191a03d73ce2da6eea4"}},"id":"prt_f047d1efd001BcpTMVMb4YdNzB","sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","messageID":"msg_f047ca61a001M3YZVXQ6tAVfWq"}}
