{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1782486867578,"sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","part":{"id":"prt_f047f1e79001x0U9Q0YRetygMu","messageID":"msg_f047f16aa001XR6HS7hVLjkfsa","sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","snapshot":"7703cce27f1b943689f3db47fd8eb26992742050","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1782486901137,"sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","part":{"id":"prt_f047f6bc9001jzqDq6SerYZGV7","messageID":"msg_f047f16aa001XR6HS7hVLjkfsa","sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","type":"text","text":"The YAML’s spec writeback, memory save, and git staging would write outside the bound lineage directory, conflicting with the user’s explicit path constraint; I’ll execute init, one iteration, reducer-equivalent state refresh, and synthesis only inside the lineage artifact directory.","time":{"start":1782486887369,"end":1782486901135},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0331373a3ec3f76a016a3e97674eac819591262668b39d426d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
