{"type":"text","timestamp":1782486925253,"sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","part":{"id":"prt_f047fd5430011IvJMwJs5g0s1U","messageID":"msg_f047fa6730012ioe6vr3iu0uHP","sessionID":"ses_0fb835c90ffeqUAmvkS8gfEWSy","type":"text","text":"The external glob came back empty despite the documented path, so I’m checking the corpus directory directly and narrowing the current-skill inventory to the five mode packets plus their `references/` and `assets/`.","time":{"start":1782486914371,"end":1782486925252},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_03007039ff770dc7016a3e97824fa48191a967ff2869593139","phase":"commentary"}}}}
